comments: Brown (BOS) sets the screen on Nurkic (POR) and does not deliver contact.
McCollum (POR) makes marginal contact with Hayward (BOS) after he releases the shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) and McCollum (POR) briefly engage and disengage during the screen.
Theis (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Nurkic (POR) and absorbs the contact after Tatum (BOS) makes clean contact with the ball.
Smart (BOS) sets the screen on Nurkic (POR) and does not deliver contact.
McCollum (POR) wraps Hayward (BOS) and affects his FOM.
Nurkic (POR) sets the screen on Tatum (BOS) and does not deliver contact.
Lillard (POR) makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) on the perimeter.
Lillard (POR) makes marginal contact with Tatum (BOS) while attempting the steal.
Theis (BOS) maintains a legal guarding position on Nurkic (POR) in the post.
Tatum (BOS) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Anthony (POR) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) makes marginal contact with Hayward (BOS) as he receives the pass.

The ball crosses the plane of the midcourt line, changing its status from backcourt to frontcourt on the pass by Tatum (BOS).  Hayward (BOS) then receives the pass after having his foot planted in the backcourt and never establishing position in the frontcourt.  This is a correctly called backcourt violation and it is not a reviewable matter.
Hayward (BOS) makes marginal contact with Trent Jr. (POR) as he receives the throw-in.
Lillard (POR) and Smart (BOS) briefly engage and Lillard releases from the contact to receive the pass.
Nurkic (POR) sets the screen on Smart (BOS) and does not deliver contact.
Theis (BOS) makes contact with Nurkic's (POR) head while going for the loose ball.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Hayward (BOS).
Anthony (POR) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
